<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Thrust1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Thrust,</orth> subst. an attack with the point of a sharp weapon; opposed to blow: <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.21" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 1, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.173" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 1, 173</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.1.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 1, 24</bibl>. <cit><quote>to make a t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.228" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 228</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 1, 105</bibl>. <cit><quote>interchanging --s and blows,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.120" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 120</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>at blow and t.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.238" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 238</bibl></cit>.
